text: Jacob Wukie (born May 11, 1986) is an American athlete.Jacob Wukie at NBCOlympics.com ; retrieved 2012-8-13. He is best known as an archer who competed in the Summer Olympic Games.SportsReference.com (SR/Olympics), "Jacob Wukie" ; retrieved 2012-7-31. ==Career== At the 2012 Summer Olympics, he was part of the men's archery team that won a silver medal. ==Related pages== * United States at the Olympics * Brady Ellison * Jake Kaminski ==References== ==Other websites== * Jacob Wukie at London2012.com Category:1986 births Category:Living people Category:American archers Category:Olympic silver medalists for the United States Category:Sportspeople from Ohio Category:People from Massillon, Ohio
